meta_description: Sink into the Scene of the Second Saturday ArtWalk
post_content: St. Pete is an art lover's paradise in an actual paradise. If art is what you need, then the second Saturday of every month is when you should feed. Second Saturday ArtWalk takes place each month and spans across five different cultural districts in St. Pete. Over 200 artists participate in this monthly event as well as 40 art galleries that keep their doors open extra late into the evening.
